<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>298</hymn_number>
<title>Yesu Ya Sauko Nan, Halleluya LW298</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1) Yesu ya sauko nan, Halleluya, Amin,
 Domin mu batattu, Halleluya, Amin.
 Shi ne mai ƙaunarmu, abokin faɗaɗɗu,
 Sarkin amintattu, Halleluya, Amin.

[V2]
 2) Yesu ya nemo mu, Halleluya, Amin,
 Yesu ya cece mu, Halleluya, Amin.
 Shi ne Shugabanmu, shi ne zai bi da mu
 Tsoro kuwa ba ma ji, Halleluya, Amin.

[V3]
 3) Yesu ya koma can, Halleluya, Amin,
 Yesu Mai Cetonmu, Halleluya, Amin. Masoyinmu ne shi, can Sama za mu yi
 Waƙa mai daɗin ji, Halleluya, Amin</lyrics>
</song>